  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators planned to study the etiopathogenic factors of conotruncal cardiac defects
      regarding the relations between the metabolic, the genetic and the environmental factors
      which lead to these cardiopathy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
